{"tid":2239700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"直擊集體吸毒公園集體啪針 警車在場拆家照賣毒品","createTime":"2020-10-12T07:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:52:54.000Z","uid":86509,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8a49dfc2928963db10ddc5eaff0eba6ca483d23d","tid":2239700,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eAvevTA4Dp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeAvevTA4Dp0&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=756a8dff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eAvevTA4Dp0</a><br />\n<br />\n每天早上七時許，二十多名癮君子買完毒品，以及在附近士多買針筒後，便會聚集在深水埗醫局街南昌街交界的公園。他們有男有女，將毒品注入針筒後，便公然脫下褲子，就在公園內打針吸毒，即是有途人行過，他們也置之不理。完事後，他們便把針筒掉在地上或草叢內，有些針筒還染有血跡，十分恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 全文：<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/gGBvAueL39\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FgGBvAueL39&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=f613987b\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/gGBvAueL39</a>"},{"pid":"38d678d4d80c2d1c1d75a0e3bc0cfcef26ae2881","tid":2239700,"uid":86509,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"除咗警察本身係拆家睇場<br />\n真係諗唔到第二個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cccbc9a12b21b160b3f0cedb444963c7d5a83a","tid":2239700,"uid":54800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"林大總統又發聲: Green object 响警車上面暗中觀察, 啱時機先會衝出黎..._  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d0c23dc17ad724846a4bc7f2dddb32ffc3ff88","tid":2239700,"uid":224066,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scogka4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fscogka4.jpg&h=3038d3f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d5004060b46ae08e2595b6b0a3382828614a9c9","tid":2239700,"uid":77717,"like":10,"dislike":0,"s